{"tid":911614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★蝗蟲日！【一田優惠日】內地客凌晨廣州搭和諧號出發掃貨","createTime":"2018-11-22T04:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T06:04:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58aac0fb3dedc4e46ccec72550a214485d1437f1","tid":911614,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2122269/org/6961b58833dc6c448e07ab37a4a9af6d.JPG/szLaBVrKhYeNYPq8PudjpIn16YwF_bBU6vFyyM_xcsg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2122269%2Forg%2F6961b58833dc6c448e07ab37a4a9af6d.JPG%2FszLaBVrKhYeNYPq8PudjpIn16YwF_bBU6vFyyM_xcsg&h=973c2270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每逢「一田購物優惠日」總吸引不少市民及內地客拖篋掃貨，未正式開始營業，門外已「打蛇餅」。有內地旅客凌晨4時從廣州出發，來港只為到一田掃貨，坦言「港貨有信心保證、價格有折扣」。<br />\n<br />\n一田百貨於今日至26日舉行購物優惠日，剛開始營業店內已人頭湧湧，不少特價電器被搶空，但人流未如崇光百貨感謝周般擠擁得水泄不通，通道尚算暢順。<br />\n<br />\n廣州客：每年均搭和諧號「掃貨」<br />\n<br />\n來自廣州的梁先生在開店約兩小時已搶購電飯煲、衣服、背囊等，坦言每年一田促銷均乘搭和諧號來港「掃貨」，今年清晨4時出門乘搭頭班車，約8時半抵達沙田，排隊入場也用了十多分鐘，主要購買「啱心水」商品，下午即回廣州。他認為，港貨有信心保證、價格有折扣，預計每次消費4、5千元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣州譚先生：計算匯率　如同折上折<br />\n<br />\n同樣來自廣州的譚先生表示，「本身（一田）有折頭打，加上匯率就折上折，抵就自然多人買」。他又指，香港商品種類多元化，今早掃了不少玩具給兩個兒子，下月作聖誕禮物送出，也預計今日會花上4、5千元。他說，每年均來一田掃貨，「邊啲抵就買邊啲，有需要就買」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n位於三樓的購物區，不少市民搶購玩具及行李箱，來自江西的何小姐表示，從網上得知有一田優惠日，特意來買了3個28吋行李箱，直言「好抵買」，較正價便宜一大半，預計只花約一千元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/262112/%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B0%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0%E6%97%A5-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E%E6%90%AD%E5%92%8C%E8%AB%A7%E8%99%9F%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E6%8E%83%E8%B2%A8-%E6%B8%AF%E8%B2%A8%E6%9C%89%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F262112%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%2584%25AA%25E6%2583%25A0%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2587%258C%25E6%2599%25A8%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25B7%259E%25E6%2590%25AD%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25AB%25A7%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%258E%2583%25E8%25B2%25A8-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%2589&d=dfeeB01biWcpSatpjJUPM%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=8fe8e94f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/262112/%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B0%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0%E6%97%A5-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E%E6%90%AD%E5%92%8C%E8%AB%A7%E8%99%9F%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E6%8E%83%E8%B2%A8-%E6%B8%AF%E8%B2%A8%E6%9C%89%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89</a>"},{"pid":"e3aa0dd2d5ac34cc922960faea4de894b27e47da","tid":911614,"uid":106348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"大逆不道，我國出產無信心保證咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6a71728d1ddb52fbb164b4653439b9e349ea04","tid":911614,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"成班走狗垃圾"},{"pid":"829a93b4df535e36f518350103562e4b737f20d7","tid":911614,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"來自日本的一田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f5def1174a8e0529cb04a61bdab8b16362ccb0","tid":911614,"uid":8187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有內地旅客凌晨4時從廣州出發，來港只為到一田掃貨，坦言「港貨有信心保證、價格有折扣」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔用國貨，拉去打靶啦"},{"pid":"a8593c5af510cefd181422ccedac332e87aa5b49","tid":911614,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"829a93b4df535e36f518350103562e4b737f20d7","tid":911614,"uid":46947